    <briefdescription>
<para>A partitioner that splits the ranges until it identifies we are not moving to new threads. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This partitioner splits the ranges until it identifies we are not moving to new threads. Apart from that, it behaves as a <ref refid="classfutures_1_1halve__partitioner" kindref="compound">halve_partitioner</ref>, splitting the range up to a minimum grain size. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
